Author: davidw
Content:
For me, these invite sarcasm:

"Make yourself a blend of fruits that excite you. I love a carrot-apple-ginger juice and drink it in the morning"

I like a blend of various fermented grapes, but am not yet to the point where i drink it in the morning.
